      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Dahwids zehlehs/ un\nnogahje ar wiffeem teem Lau-\ndim/kas pee winna bija/ no teem\nNamneekem Juhda/ ka tas no\nturren ustwestu to Deewa Schkir-\nstu/ pee ka tas Wahrs tohp pee-\ntauks/ tas Wahrs ta KUN-\nGA Zebāat/ kas us teem Keru-\nbini dshwo.\n"
