      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tee nu winzu no Abi-\nnadaba Namma/ kas us to Pa-\nkalnu irr/ ar to Deewa Schkirstu\nrehme/ tad gahje Atijus preeksch\nta Schkirsta.\n"
